TextBody:
Hello Todd,
 
Thank you for contacting Netwrix Technical Support. My name is Frantz, and I will work with you to help you upgrade to the latest version.
 
We will have a few meetings. The first is the preflight meeting; in that meeting, I will review the current setting and different jobs running, advise you accordingly, and discuss the upgrade.
 
Please use the link below to schedule the preflight meeting.
https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=SzM8gsdm0kH8hgt.4F1ViU9gHotUy2y9O464EudNQq0-Z&MeetingID=AE6Y6n_ivRNrN294eYSGO6uj_KAsnSw_1Lw6Cf3k_zA-Z
 
Thanks,


Frantz Jean Baptiste

TextBody:
Hi Todd,
 
Thank you for your time today.
I did the preflight in today's meeting and reviewed the current setting.
I also upgraded the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor and the Access Information Center to the latest version.
The upgrade went well, and I advised you to log in to the report and AIC sites to ensure you have access.
